{"tid":2052330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"足總主席： 研究設黑名單 噓國歌或被禁不能進入球場","createTime":"2020-06-05T12:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T17:57:22.000Z","uid":22556,"like":20,"dislike":185,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e02cfe24966461cb091cd13ec9793185514e5e","tid":2052330,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"貝鈞奇今早出席立法帳委會公開聆訊，其後再被追問具爭議的國歌法草案。他表示， 場內球迷噓國歌，在近年經常發生，甚至令足總被多次罰款，又形容足總在此事上都是受害者，他亦藉此再次強調，不應把政治帶入球賽。近日有報道指，足總擬訂出黑名單，禁止滋事球迷入場。貝鈞奇未有談及黑名單的推行實際計劃，但指全球不少地方的足球總會都有類似做法，用以阻止屢勸不改的球迷進場生事。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200605/32AF3C2WBAY3IOVPUFAAEKSQRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200605%2F32AF3C2WBAY3IOVPUFAAEKSQRI%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=f9e50fbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200605%2F32AF3C2WBAY3IOVPUFAAEKSQRI%2F&h=57535855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200605/32AF3C2WBAY3IOVPUFAAEKSQRI/</a>"},{"pid":"8271334f6568d8b87d00fb79f400bbae99049f0e","tid":2052330,"uid":35919,"like":247,"dislike":1,"score":246,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"本身已經冇人睇 淨低嗰啲都趕走埋 搵鬼睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63074fddfe9657b863dc275a6a510a2c4e8cd744","tid":2052330,"uid":198278,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"開始倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fadf085c134dbf3e11b6786f0ed394ee3061a1","tid":2052330,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:34:28.000Z","msg":"戴口罩"},{"pid":"de3a04725919856c0a679f0a57fb855f1e6b46d0","tid":2052330,"uid":75610,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:34:49.000Z","msg":"本身已經坐唔爆<img src=\"/assets/faces